      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera features the refined 3.6L M96 flat-six, delivering linear power delivery and a distinct boxer note. The IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a ceramic retrofit. The 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp engagement, complemented by a factory-optioned limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders. A mechanically sound driver\u2019s car optimized for the purist.",
